## TS7006 (implicit any on EVM event handler params) — 60 errors

These all come from the H09 fix wave which added EVM `.events.on('step'|'newContract'|'beforeMessage'|'afterMessage', (a, next) => ...)` handlers without JSDoc types. Apply consistent JSDoc annotations across all five files. Look at the existing tracer types in packages/actions/src/common/ (e.g., DebugTraceCallResult, TraceCall handlers) to know the right types:

